com.ibm.mobile.services.location.objects

Class IBMPointOfInterest

  • java.lang.Object
    • IBMDataObject
      • com.ibm.mobile.services.location.objects.IBMPointOfInterest

  • public class IBMPointOfInterest
extends IBMDataObject
    IBMPointOfInterest objects are IBMDataObject specializations describing virtual parameters on a map. This interface defines methods for interacting with points of interest. The IBMPointOfInterest class is a provisional API. APIs that are marked provisional are evolving and might change or be removed in future releases.
